The synaptic weight change is:

\Delta w = A_+ e^{-\Delta t / \tau_+} \quad \text{for } \Delta t > 0

\Delta w = -A_- e^{\Delta t / \tau_-} \quad \text{for } \Delta t < 0

By pairing taVNS with prefrontal activation (e.g., during an interoceptive attention task), we selectively strengthen the bidirectional pathway.

